                                                    <%= order.orderedItems.product.productName %>
                                                </a></h5> <span class="product-qty">x <%=
                                                    order.orderedItems.product.productQuantity %></span>
                                        </td>
                                        <td>Rs. <%= order.orderedItems.product.productQuantity *
